sentences.sContent: But the problem here is that this draft appears to have been canonised, passing largely unedited into popular conscience.
sentences.sContent_eng: But the problem here is that this draft appears to have been canonised, passing largely unedited into popular conscience.
sentences.sCn: 但现在的问题是，这份初稿似乎已被奉为圣典，大部分内容未经校对就化入了公众的良知。

synos.tran: 未刊行的；未编辑的；未经审查的
